AsciiCommander - Class in com.uk.tsl.rfid.asciiprotocol
AsciiCommander provides methods to communicate with TSL devices that use the TSL ASCII 2.0 Protocol Instances of this class support: connection and disconnection from any TSL Reader connected via bluetooth execution of an IAsciiCommand either synchronously or asynchronously management of the responder chain for data received from the TSL device Warning: Instances of AsciiCommander MUST be created on the UI thread
